24#include <sys/cdefs.h>
25__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_engine_gr_ctxgm20b.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:32 riastradh Exp $");
26
27#include "ctxgf100.h"
28
29static void
30gm20b_grctx_generate_r406028(struct gf100_gr *gr)
31{
32 struct nvkm_device *device = gr->base.engine.subdev.device;
33 u32 tpc_per_gpc = 0;
34 int i;
35
36 for (i = 0; i < gr->gpc_nr; i++)
37 tpc_per_gpc |= gr->tpc_nr[i] << (4 * i);
38
39 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x406028, tpc_per_gpc);
40 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x405870, tpc_per_gpc);
41}
42
43static void
44gm20b_grctx_generate_main(struct gf100_gr *gr, struct gf100_grctx *info)
45{
46 struct nvkm_device *device = gr->base.engine.subdev.device;
47 const struct gf100_grctx_func *grctx = gr->func->grctx;
48 int idle_timeout_save;
49 int i, tmp;
50
51 gf100_gr_mmio(gr, gr->fuc_sw_ctx);
52
53 gf100_gr_wait_idle(gr);
54
55 idle_timeout_save = nvkm_rd32(device, 0x404154);
56 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x404154, 0x00000000);
57
58 grctx->attrib(info);
59
60 grctx->unkn(gr);
61
62 gm204_grctx_generate_tpcid(gr);
63 gm20b_grctx_generate_r406028(gr);
64 gk104_grctx_generate_r418bb8(gr);
65
66 for (i = 0; i < 8; i++)
67 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x4064d0 + (i * 0x04), 0x00000000);
68
69 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x405b00, (gr->tpc_total << 8) | gr->gpc_nr);
70
71 gk104_grctx_generate_rop_active_fbps(gr);
72 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x408908, nvkm_rd32(device, 0x410108) | 0x80000000);
73
74 for (tmp = 0, i = 0; i < gr->gpc_nr; i++)
75 tmp |= ((1 << gr->tpc_nr[i]) - 1) << (i * 4);
76 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x4041c4, tmp);
77
78 gm204_grctx_generate_405b60(gr);
79
80 gf100_gr_wait_idle(gr);
81
82 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x404154, idle_timeout_save);
83 gf100_gr_wait_idle(gr);
84
85 gf100_gr_mthd(gr, gr->fuc_method);
86 gf100_gr_wait_idle(gr);
87
88 gf100_gr_icmd(gr, gr->fuc_bundle);
89 grctx->pagepool(info);
90 grctx->bundle(info);
91}
92
93const struct gf100_grctx_func
94gm20b_grctx = {
95 .main = gm20b_grctx_generate_main,
96 .unkn = gk104_grctx_generate_unkn,
97 .bundle = gm107_grctx_generate_bundle,
98 .bundle_size = 0x1800,
99 .bundle_min_gpm_fifo_depth = 0x182,
100 .bundle_token_limit = 0x1c0,
101 .pagepool = gm107_grctx_generate_pagepool,
102 .pagepool_size = 0x8000,
103 .attrib = gm107_grctx_generate_attrib,
104 .attrib_nr_max = 0x600,
105 .attrib_nr = 0x400,
106 .alpha_nr_max = 0xc00,
107 .alpha_nr = 0x800,
108};
